snippet.title: PC Longplay [932] Soul Gambler
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Ravenlord

Soul Gambler puts you in the role of Faust, an ordinary young man living in the present day whose destiny is about to be change forever.

The game doesn't have resolution options so it records automatically in 1080p, however the game is 4:3 so I cut those black extra borders, that is why video is in such strange resolution. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
